data.description: Amazing home in Country Meadows with curb appeal! Just minutes to I-215 Freeway, amazing restaurants and shopping. Walking distance to neighborhood parks and elementary schools. Floors recently replaced with plank wood. The formal living room has Beautiful vaulted ceilings. The upgraded kitchen offers ample cabinetry, granite countertops with custom Backsplash and large Center Island with bar seating. Bedrooms are located on the second floor with a large loft perfect for an office, playroom or movie room.
